{"tid":1452469,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維也納公約第39條 (戰時罪行)- 偽裝敵方人員","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:27:28.000Z","uid":268814,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba8a097c1f9c486e31956fcb93ad1c10d3de1a8","tid":1452469,"uid":268814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"Geneva Convention<br />\n<br />\nArticle 39. &ndash; Emblems of nationality<br />\n<br />\n1. It is prohibited to make use in an armed conflict of the flags or military emblems, insignia or uniforms of neutral or other States not Parties to the conflict.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. It is prohibited to make use of the flags or military emblems, insignia or uniforms of adverse Parties while engaging in attacks or to shield, favour, protect or impede military operations.</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ddaf93d6bf14fedd21aeb7bf65260e8905a578b","tid":1452469,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95f8674846de5e824cae2a930c4223afb2617cb","tid":1452469,"uid":66905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}